BT 1 0 0 1 61.2 611 Tm (1. BUSINESS MODEL PRINCIPLE) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 61.2 590 Tm (Aura operates as civic communication infrastructure.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 61.2 569 Tm (The platform prioritizes record continuity, identity-bound discourse, institutional) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 61.2 555 Tm (accountability, and chronological communication.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 61.2 534 Tm (Revenue mechanisms must not violate these principles.) Tj T* ET
